          <span class="fs-nl-cap">Hand-raised in Midland, TX</span>
        </div>
        <div class="fs-nl-body">
          <p class="fs-nl-eyebrow">Clutch alerts</p>
          <h3 class="fs-nl-h">Rather skip the incubator? Get chick alerts.</h3>
          <p class="fs-nl-sub">One short email the moment a new hand-raised Congo or Timneh chick — or a candled fertile clutch — opens for reservation. No incubator, no risk, just first pick.</p>
          <form class="fs-nl-form" action="https://formspree.io/f/xrejpnvn" method="POST">
            <input type="email" name="email" required placeholder="you@email.com" aria-label="Email address for chick alerts" />
