        <h3 class="cag-h3">Prefer a breeding pair or the fertile eggs themselves?</h3>
        <p>Established aviaries write us about our proven-producing African Grey pair, and experienced incubator keepers ask for the candled fertile hatching eggs directly — both are in the grid above, and both carry the same documentation stack as our companion birds. <a href="/available/">Our full available-birds page</a> lists everything currently reservable.</p>
